iss, L. Schultz, J. L. Lombardi, and F. B. Prinz, “Layered Manufacturing Material Issues for SDM of Polymers and Ceramics,” Proceedings of the Solid Freeform Fabrication Symposium, The University of Texas at Austin, Austin, Texas, August 1997.【15】	Beck, J.E., Prinz, F.B., Siewiorek, D.P., and Weiss, L.E., “Manufacturing Mechatronics Using Thermal Spray Shape Deposition,” Solid Freeform Fabrication Symposium, The University of Texas At Austin, August, 1992.【16】	Cham, J.G.; Pruitt, B.L.; Cutkosky, M.R.; Binnard, M.; Weiss, L.E.; Neplotnik, and G., “Layered manufacturing with embedded components: process planning issues,” Proceedings of the 1999 ASME DETC/DFM Conference, Las Vegas, Nevada, Sept 12-15, 1999.【17】	Clark, J. E., Cham, J. G., Bailey, S. A., Froehlich, E. M., Full, R. J. , and Cutkosky, M. R., “Biomimetic Design and Fabrication of a Hexapedal Running Robot,” IEEE International Conference on Robotics and Automation, Seoul, Korea, May 21-26, 2001.【18】	R.I.King and J.G.Mcdonald, ”Product Design Implications of new High-Speed Milling Techniques,” J. of Eng. For Ind, p.1170, 1976.【19】	永進機械, (http://www.supermax.com.tw/chinese/init.jsp? include=foundry.jsp).【20】	Draganfly Innovations RCToys, (http://www.rctoys.com/ rc-toys- and-parts/DF-Eyecam/RC-PARTS-WIRELESS-VIDEO-KITS.hl).【21】	東芝半導體公司, (http:// www.semicon.toshiba.co.jp/openb2b/ websearch/productDetails.jsp?partKey=TA7279P).【22】	勝特力科技有限公司, (http://www.100y.com.tw/ viewproduct.asp? MNo=1642).【23】	無線電界雜誌社, “電晶體電路製作集錦(一),” 1993.【24】	The Machine Intelligence Laboratory at the University of Florida, (http://www.mil.ufl.edu/subjugator/comp8_main.html).【25】	The Australian National University, (http:// www.seaswarm.com.au/).【26】	林育洲, “軸流風扇之數值與實驗分析,” 臺灣科技大學機械工程研究所碩士論文, 1998年.【27】	林鴻志, “Pentium 4 處理器冷卻風扇之製造與實驗研究,” 臺灣科技大學機械工程研究所碩士論文, 2001年.【28】	顧哲安, “筆記型電腦之風扇設計與振動分析,” 成功大學機械工程研究所碩士論文, 2001年.【29】	System 3R, (http://www.system3r.com/), Products→Preision Manufacturing Standard program→Dynafix→Chucks→3R-770-1.【30】	System 3R,